Emily shares four steps for overcoming jealousy. You can get past jealousy in most situations if you can get over your insecurities. Also, find out why she's really moaning during sex, what to say in your first online dating message, how to deal with body image issues, and if there’s a platonic dating site for those who don’t want to get down.
